oach Tunnels','MTR Corporation Limited','17 December 2012 - 18 November 2018','<p>The Shatin to Central Link (SCL) is a government funded concessionary project providing a strategic rail corridor from Shatin to Central. One of the contracts of the Shatin to Central Link (SCL). The scope of work is included Tunnels Works, Foundation Works, Site Formation Works, Bridge Works, Noise Enclosure Works and Demolition Works. This is a challenging project in terms of geographical location and work complexity, as this construction site will passes through the aged urban town Hung Hom where a huge amount of utilities are underground. Due to the location, extensive TTM arrangements and utilities diversion and/or protection has to be undertaken.</p>','2025-06-02 07:59:55.496000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.144000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.376000',15,36,'en',3.00),(399,'pdr9lgsdmjkmipq66km4xrh0','合约编号 DC/2009/24净化海港计划第二期甲 - 沙湾, 数码港, 华富, 香港仔及鸭脷洲初级污水处理厂改善工程','合约编号 DC/2009/24净化海港计划第二期甲 - 沙湾, 数码港, 华富, 香港仔及鸭脷洲初级污水处理厂改善工程\n\n','香港特别行政区 - 渠务署','2011 年 08 月 31 日 - 2018 年 01 月 08 日','<p>为了改善维多利亚港水质，净化海港计划 于八十年代后期开始分阶段展开，用以收集及处理维港两岸区域的污水。自净化海港计划第一期于2001年底启用后，维港水质有明显的改善。第二期分为两个阶段 : 分别是第二期甲和第二期乙。</p><p>合约DC/2009/24为第二期甲主体工程之一，工程内容包括在沙湾、数码港、华富、香港仔及鸭利洲之初级污水处理厂内建造隔筛、砂砾收集器、除臭室、工场和行政大楼以及改建现有入水泵房。</p>','2025-06-03 02:16:24.198000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.209000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.427000',15,36,'zh-CN',6.00),(400,'m633u51puu7yr313mbaw6ika','白石角发展计划基础设施工程 - 第 2A 阶段 (合约编号: TP37/03)','白石角发展计划基础设施工程 - 第 2A 阶段','土木工程拓展署','2004 年 06 月 29 日 - 2008 年 10 月 15 日','<p>白石角发展计划基础设施工程 主要工程项目包括地盘平整工程，以及道路和桥梁建设，自行车道，海滨长廊，人行隧道，及相关的环境美化工程等</p>','2025-06-03 03:30:36.756000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.333000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.521000',15,36,'zh-CN',19.00),(401,'vqegjzdb5ovadvuv6eoupxjv','Drainage Improvement in East Kowloon - Package A (Contract No. DC/2004/03)','Drainage Improvement in East Kowloon - Package A\n\n','Drainage Services Department','11 May 2005 - 05 January 2009','<p>Major works consisted of:</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Construction of approx. 5.5km of drains with diameter ranging from 225mm to 2,400mm</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Construction of approx. 3km of watermain with diameter ranging from 100mm to 300mm along the proposed drains using the common trench approach</li></ul>','2025-06-02 08:26:54.328000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.243000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.527000',15,36,'en',17.00),(402,'cbofth62f762wky8jx3yk58k','Contract No. KL/2008/09 Kai Tak Development – Stage 1 Infrastructure Works at North Apron of Kai Tak Airport for Public Housing and Government Office Development','Contract No. KL/2008/09 Kai Tak Development – Stage 1 Infrastructure Works at North Apron of Kai Tak Airport for Public Housing and Government Office Development','Civil Engineering and Development Department','15 July 2009 - 23 August 2013','<p>The major scope of this project comprises the construction of approximately 2.6m long roads within the Project Site including the control, management, maintenance and diversion of existing roads, 2 footbridge FB1 and FB4, associated drainage including box culverts, sewerage and watermain works, enhancement and extension works of existing subways SW1, enhancement works of existing subways SW3 and SW5, landscape hardworks and softworks and environmental mitigation measures.</p><p>The works include realignment of Concorde Road, and construction of local Roads L2, L3, L4 (part) and L15. In conjunction with these roadworks are the associated street furniture, road markings and tra¬c signs, works for the highways structures (Footbridges, Subway, Enhancement Works) across Prince Edward Road East, construction of drainage, sewerage and fresh and salt water supplies systems to serve the Public Rental Housing (PRH) sites and the KTGO.</p><p>The works also include construction of two box culverts BC1 &amp; BC2, a 2.5m x 2.5m box culvert at Road L3 and its connection to the existing Nullah No. 2 and 3.0m x 2.8m box culvert along the amenity strip of Road L2 and its connection to the existing Kai Tak Nullah respectively, demolition of an existing ramp at the EMSD Headquarters ramp at the EMSD Headquarters crossing the Cargo Circuit, abandon the existing Nullah No. 1 and pipes, construction of 5 footpath connections from Road L2 to Subway SW5 and Wang Kong Road, improvement works at Kai Shing Street / Kai Wah Street junction, construction and installation of electrical and mechanical works for the infrastructure serving the early development at the North Apron area including the PRH sites and KTGO, landscape softworks and landscape hardworks.</p>','2025-06-02 08:09:56.473000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.333000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.560000',15,36,'en',8.00),(403,'e7yl3k0at9pnsnz1gh0xpvpd','铜锣湾行车天桥重建及相关的维园道扩阔工程 (合约编号：HY/2003/27)','铜锣湾行车天桥重建及相关的维园道扩阔工程','路政署','2004 年 06 月 10 日 - 2008 年 05 月 29 日','<p>工 程 计 划 包 括:</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>拆 卸 现 有 的 铜 锣 湾 行 车 天 桥 和 毗 邻 的 行 人 天 桥 ；</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建 造 一 条 连 接 东 行 的 维 园 道 与 南 行 之 告 士 打 道 的 210 米 长 的 双 线 单 程 行 车 天 桥 ；</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建 造 一 条 横 跨 维 园 道 的 有 盖 行 人 天 桥 ；</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>为 维 园 道 西 行 线 一 条 170 米 长 的 路 段 重 新 定 线 并 扩 阔 为 5 条 行 车 线 ；</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>为 维 园 道 东 行 线 一 条 225 米 长 的 路 段 重 新 定 线 ； 以 及</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>进 行 包 括 环 境 美 化 工 程 之 相 关 工 程 。</li></ul>','2025-06-03 03:32:08.295000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.340000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.613000',15,36,'zh-CN',20.00),(404,'zddshtdytbm2lw048oe1imcg','Contract No. HK/2012/08 – Wan Chai Development Phase II – Central – Wan Chai Bypass at Wan Chai West','Contract No. HK/2012/08 – Wan Chai Development Phase II – Central – Wan Chai Bypass at Wan Chai West','Civil Engineering and Development Department','31 January 2013 - 28 November 2018','<p>The key purpose of Wan Chai Development Phase II is to provide land at Wan Chai North and North Point for the construction of the Central - Wan Chai Bypass and Island Eastern Corridor Link. Land formed under the project will be developed as a world-class waterfront promenade for public enjoyment and solve the traffic problem around Wan Chai district.</p><p>This is one of the contract in Wan Chai Development Phase II. It is a large scale Reclamation Project with more than 5 Ha. in size. The Project&#x27;s location is from the Central Reclamation Phase III (CRIII) eastern seawall to the west of Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Centre Extension. The scope of work includes dredging works, seawall works, watermains laying, demolition of existing Expo Drive West Bridge, box culvert extension and stormwater drainage works.</p>','2025-06-02 07:57:34.832000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.619000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.856000',15,36,'en',2.00),(405,'blufpdmwqmp7p740k3zzpf3y','Civil Engineering and Development Department Contract No. CV/2013/08 Liantang / Heung Yuen Wai Boundary Control Point Site Formation and Infrastructure Works – Contract 6','Civil Engineering and Development Department Contract No. CV/2013/08 Liantang / Heung Yuen Wai Boundary Control Point Site Formation and Infrastructure Works – Contract 6','Civil Engineering and Development Department','24 June 2015 - 21 June 2019','<p>The LT/HYW BCP is the seventh land-based BCP between Hong Kong and Shenzhen. At present, there are two land-based BCPs at Man Kam To and Sha Tau Kok. Owing to geographical constraints, however, these two BCPs have little room for further expansion. Situated between Man Kam To and Sha Tau Kok, the LT/HYW BCP will make up for the inadequacies and make cross-boundary transportation and connections between Hong Kong and the eastern part of Guangdong Province as well as the Fujian and Jiangxi Provinces more convenient and efficient. This can help expand Hong Kong&#x27;s economic hinterland.</p><p>It comprises the construction of an approximately 4.6km long dual two-lane Connecting Road connecting the BCP with the proposed Sha Tau Kok Interchange and the associated tunnel ventilation buildings. Provision of sewage collection, treatment and disposal facilities for the BCP and the resite of Chuk Yuen Village and the associated environmental mitigation measures, and Environmental Monitoring and Audit (EM&amp;A)</p>','2025-06-02 07:53:52.550000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.591000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.891000',8,36,'en',1.00),(406,'hhup866onvmd4u33bsfxg7d1','蝴蝶合初级配水库至市区次级配水库之供水设施，第一期工程—在深水埗区铺设供水管网 (合约编号： 14/WSD/98)','蝴蝶合初级配水库至市区次级配水库之供水设施，第一期工程—在深水埗区铺设供水管网','水务署','1999 年 12 月 01 日 - 2004 年 02 月 29 日','<ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>供应和铺设直径1.8米至2.2米，长约2800米的钢制焊饮用水管及相关配套工程。</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>临时和永久的公用实施管道改造工程。</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>设计和执行临时交通管理系统工程。</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>道路和排水改善工程。</li></ul>','2025-06-03 03:37:46.824000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.687000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.921000',15,36,'zh-CN',24.00),(407,'zcliqr94r8mmmyamargekuyq','屯门38区内河货柜码头 (TMTL393)','屯门38区内河货柜码头','内河码头有限公司','1996 年 11 月 01 日 - 1999 年 11 月 30 日','<p>主要工程包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>浚挖、填海及地质改善，总面积达65公顷</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造共长3.3公里之重力式垂直海墙码头及530米长防潮堤</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>重新铺设海底排污管，包括2条各长2.1公里直径1500毫米及一条730米长直径2100毫米预制排污管</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>安装850米长直径达3250毫米之3管道混凝土排水管，包括建造大型沙井室</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>排水及水管设施</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>钢结构冷冻货柜堆放架</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>供电站及电力供应设备</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>35米高灯塔及照明设备</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>码头大楼及其它码头内建筑物</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>净水及海水供应系统</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>码头内行车道及货柜运输道路</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>绿化设施</li></ul>','2025-06-03 03:48:04.756000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.874000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.060000',15,36,'zh-CN',31.00),(408,'rj61bcqedc0wxe3wnc82dxiy','美孚站 (九广铁路 西铁合约编号CC-404)','美孚站','九广铁路公司','1999 年 08 月 02 日 - 2003 年 10 月 31 日','<p>美孚站位于荔枝角公园内，采用密封式设计。其设计特色在于使车站与公园环境融为一体。车站的天台设计为空中花园，其中包括园林绿化及各种休闲设施，为邻近的大型高密度住宅区如美孚新村及清丽苑等的居民提供服务。本站的整体设计及建造，均以融入相邻居民区与环境为主题。例如：提供足够的人行道及车道从车站通往邻近的住宅区等。在建筑期间减低对居民的影响，也是一个重要的事项。所以，在建筑期间，专门修建了一条临时人行天桥横跨整个工地，为居民提供方便的来往通道。工程完成后，由于西铁的通车，美孚站及其天台上的空中花园的建成启用，大幅改善了邻近地区的交通及环境，居民的生活质素也得到相应提高。</p>','2025-06-03 03:39:55.522000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.823000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.084000',15,36,'zh-CN',26.00),(409,'iiac7f9pbp4mw4mwyf4tco60','海洋公园全新发展计划 (合约CS01 –动物医院)','海洋公园全新发展计划','香港海洋公园','2007 年 03 月 26 日 - 2008 年 10 月 31 日','<p>工程主要包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>兴建动物医院的主体建筑，包括游泳池，办公大楼及变压房</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>医院内的机电，屋宇设备，消防，电梯，通风及空调系统的安装及装饰工程</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>医院内安装公用设施，包括食水，咸水，消防水及操控电缆</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建立排水及排污系统使雨水及污水排放到附近的现有系统</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>医院内安装，检测和测试生命维持系统</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>从现有的医院运送设备与仪器到新的动物医院</li></ul>','2025-06-03 02:24:18.545000','2025-07-07 07:05:26.837000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.123000',15,36,'zh-CN',12.00),(410,'j93a9d7xpa0u7j744uw2iwdp','白石角公众卸泥填海，第三期 (合约编号：CV/98/01)','白石角公众卸泥填海，第三期','土木工程署','1998 年 12 月 30 日 - 2002 年 05 月 17 日','<p>工程包括建造700米长的斜坡式防波海堤。管理位于沙田47B区的公众填土趸船转运站。收集公众填料。在白石角填海17公顷土地及进行相关的土质处理。建造单孔箱形暗渠，