ment Department','30 April 2007 - 29 May 2009','<p>The major works in this project consisted of the construction of an approx. 400m long and 10.3m wide two-lane carriageway with a 3.5m wide footpath on both sides section of about 160m long elevated structure over Wong Chu Road was constructed with a total of about 135m of retaining wall structure at both ends of the elevated structure.</p>','2025-06-02 08:12:59.664000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.029000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.297000',15,36,'en',10.00),(414,'tpka2a66gz7m0zisgxkmw10g','凈化海港计划第二期甲 - 北角、湾仔东及中环初级污水处理厂改善工程 (合约编号. DC/2009/23)','凈化海港计划第二期甲 - 北角、湾仔东及中环初级污水处理厂改善工程','渠务署','2011 年 06 月 01 日 - 2016 年 07 月 22 日','<p>净化海港计划是透过分阶段建造污水设施，解决因城市发展而产生的海港污染问题。</p><p>此项目为凈化海港计划的其中一个工程，工程范围包括在北角、湾仔东及中环初级污水处理厂内建造精筛及砂砾收集器大楼、除臭室和行政大楼以及改建现有入水泵房。</p>','2025-06-03 02:17:20.149000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.184000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.372000',15,36,'zh-CN',7.00),(415,'ulufjyvv38kawep40immysul','昂坪污水处理厂，污水干渠及污水排放管道 (合约编号： DC/2003/01)','昂坪污水处理厂，污水干渠及污水排放管道\n\n','渠务署','2003 年 08 月 18 日 - 2006 年 03 月 09 日','<p>前往工地的信道一直为整个项目的最大挑战。由于限制车辆使用东涌道，本项目取得的许可证甚少。同时，因最接近工地的混凝土厂也需要超过一小时的车程，所以，每天混凝土的浇注量，只能限于200立方米。这限制对于工程的进度起了很大的影响。</p><br/><p>污水处理厂内的各座钢筋混凝土结构及建筑物，都呈不规则的形状。因此，虽耍采用特别设计的模板及复杂的临时支撜结构。这也为整个项目带来一定的难度。</p>','2025-06-03 03:33:13.032000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.309000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.535000',15,36,'zh-CN',21.00),(416,'uyfcy3o0xmzpb3bj6yl2k2lh','North Coal Jetty Drainage Improvement Works for Lamma Power Station (Contract No. 05/8007)','North Coal Jetty Drainage Improvement Works for Lamma Power Station\n\n','The Hong Kong Electric Co., Ltd.','10 March 2006 - 31 October 2006','<p>The major highlight of the project is the construction of the drainage system along the decking of the Coal Jetty. The drainage system included the supply and installation of 150DN / 250DN D.I. drainage pipeline and 200DN D.I. discharge pipeline for the collection of the water from the decking of the jetty contaminated during unloading of the coal. The collected effluent is then pumped via the submersible pumps with automatic control system through the discharge pipelines and discharged to the existing Effluent Treatment Plant. The designed discharge rate is about 40cu.m / hour for each sump pit.</p><br/><p>In order to install the pipelines that were designed to be hung underneath the fatty decking, with nothing but the sea underneath, a system of temporary working platform was constructed. The temporary working platform was designed to be supported by the permanent pipeline support brackets installed prior to the erection of the platform. Sections of the working platform were fabricated with steel tubular tubes on shore and transported by sampan, the only suitable means of transport underneath the Coal Jetty, to the place under the jetty where it was erected by chain blocks and fixed to the permanent pipeline support brackets. With the temporary working platform in place, the pipelines were able to be installed easily. Upon completion of the installation the temporary platform was removed by dismantling it into pieces of steel tubular tubes and then transported back to the shore, again, by sampan.</p>','2025-06-02 08:23:12.891000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.271000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.613000',15,36,'en',15.00),(417,'jhzc0nxvigyjpte2f35596lk','葵涌大白田街兴建一所18间课室的小学 (合约编号 : SS R323)','葵涌大白田街兴建一所18间课室的小学','建筑署','2007 年 04 月 30 日 - 2009 年 07 月 31 日','<p>合约包括建造一所楼高10层的小学校舍，内有18间课室及1座楼高39.50米的礼堂与及地基工程，排水工程，外部工程及其它相关设施。该小学大楼楼面面积约8,550平方米。</p>','2025-06-03 02:22:39.795000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.411000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.634000',15,36,'zh-CN',11.00),(418,'liug1oicqs0cjhlixa2iex6a','荃湾七区城门路运动场建造工程 (合约编号：SS C410)','荃湾七区城门路运动场建造工程','建筑署','1995 年 01 月 01 日 - 1998 年 01 月 02 日','<p>建造两条有盖的观众看台以及相关的排水系统，水务设施，环境美化，机电工程和体育设施。</p>','2025-06-03 03:50:46.728000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.406000','2025-07-07 07:05:27.716000',15,36,'zh-CN',33.00),(419,'ydth9vtxe2s9p5uez7ff3bxr','大埔发展项目第12及39区场地平整工程 (合约编号：TP28/95)','大埔发展项目第12及39区场地平整工程','拓展署','1998 年 03 月 18 日 - 2